room_title: Escape room "Diner 79" by Mississippi Mind Trap Escape Room in Hannibal
room_description: Diner 79 has been a relic around these parts for years, but lately, people have been gettin sick after eatin the grub. One has even died! Speculation is that one of the servers is poisoning the food. Thank goodness the owner's adult kids have come to town to get this mystery figured out before there's another victim!
